member.remarks:
The class uses BT709 algorithm to convert color image
            to grayscale. The conversion coefficients are:
            

Red: 0.2125;

Green: 0.7154;

Blue: 0.0721.

The class uses R-Y algorithm to convert color image
            to grayscale. The conversion coefficients are:
            

Red: 0.5;

Green: 0.419;

Blue: 0.081.

The class uses Y algorithm to convert color image
            to grayscale. The conversion coefficients are:
            

Red: 0.299;

Green: 0.587;

Blue: 0.114.
